<%= link_to 'New Organization', new_organization_path, {:class => 'btn btn-danger', :style=>'float:right;margin-right:75px;',:type => 'button'} %>
<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>
Welcome to HoleInOnePointO!<br/>
<br/>
This is a site dedicated to helping golf leagues manage and present league scores and data to members FREE OF CHARGE!
<br/><br/>
Hope you enjoy the site!  Please visit us on facebook at <a href="https://www.facebook.com/holeinonepointo/" target="_blank">https://www.facebook.com/holeinonepointo/</a>
if you find interest and would like to start managing your own league or introduce your course pro to our site.

<p/>

<table class='table table-bordered'>
  <tr>
    <% Organization.columns.reject { |col| ["created_at", "updated_at", "id"].include?(col.name) }.each do |col| %>
        <th><%= col.human_name %></th>
    <% end %>

  </tr>

  <% @organizations.each_with_index do |organization,i| %>
      <tr class='<%= i.odd? ? 'warning' : 'success' %>'>
        <td><%= link_to organization.name, organization_path(organization.id) %></td>
        <td><%= organization.city %></td>
        <td><%= organization.state.name%></td>
      </tr>
  <% end %>
</table>

<br/>


